## Why this fits the system (authoring gate)

**Frontier-now:** Prevents re-introducing P0 patterns the SOLID audit found (sibling module imports, app→API source imports, cross-segment app imports, fat routes). Pairs with `46-web-route-shape`, `47-prisma-multischema`, B5/WS5 boundaries lint, and WS6 client-safe imports.

**Local-subagent-future:** Optional readonly `coupling-boundary-verifier` subagent wrapping `npm run audit:solid-inventory` — deferred; revisit if inventory-only signal proves insufficient post-B5/WS5.
